        <updateDate>2006-02-11T15:38:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Prescription Drug Safety and Affordability Act of 2006 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to deny prescription drug manufacturers a tax deduction for gifts to physicians, including gifts of meals, sponsored teachings, symposia, and travel (but not including product samples). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
